article.headline: Adams-Woods scores 25 in Saint Bonaventure's 94-60 victory over Niagara
article.description: — Mika Adams-Woods scored 25 points as Saint Bonaventure beat Niagara 94-60 on Wednesday night.
article.linkText: Adams-Woods scores 25 in Saint Bonaventure's 94-60 victory over Niagara
article.story: LEWISTON, N.Y. -- — Mika Adams-Woods scored 25 points as Saint Bonaventure beat Niagara 94-60 on Wednesday night. Adams-Woods added five assists for the Bonnies (6-2). Noel Brown scored 15 points, finishing 7 of 7 from the floor. Chad Venning had 14 points and shot 5 of 11 from the field and 4 for 5 from the foul line. Ahmad Henderson II finished with 13 points for the Purple Eagles (1-6). Randy Tucker added 10 points for Niagara. Quandre Bullock also put up 10 points. ------ The Associated Press created this story using technology provided by Data Skrive and data from Sportradar.
